title: Kubernetes replicas
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the number of replicas in a Kubernetes stateful set.
 The state of the check is dependent on the configuration of the stateful set
 in Kubernetes.

 The check returns {OK} if every replica is ready, {WARN} otherwise.

inventory:
 One service is created.

